                      "Other Minority", "Noncitizen",
                      "Republican Party ID", "Conservative Ideology",
                      "Church Attendance",
                      "Income/Capita", "Percent Black",
                      "Bush Vote, 2004", "Population")) +
     theme_bw() + xlab("Coefficient Estimate") + ylab("") +
